languages.text: "Я избавил{mf|ся|ась} от порождений псайкера. Идира жива — обеспечьте ей медпомощь, а затем приставьте надзирателя. Если она вновь поддастся влиянию варпа — стрелять без предупреждения".
"I got rid of the psyker's creations. Idira is alive — see that she gets medical attention, and then put a guard on her. If she succumbs to the warp's influence again — shoot her without warning."

languages.text: “我已经消灭了灵能者的造物，而且伊迪拉还活着。派人对她进行治疗，再派几个人把她盯紧。如果她再次受到亚空间的影响，当场枪毙。”

languages.text: «Me he librado de las creaciones de la psíquica. Idira está viva; asegúrese de que recibe atención médica y asígnele guardias. Si vuelve a sucumbir a la influencia de la disformidad, que disparen de inmediato».
languages.original_text: "I got rid of the psyker's creations. Idira is alive — see that she gets medical attention, and then put a guard on her. If she succumbs to the warp's influence again — shoot her without warning."

languages.text: 「異能者の創造物は始末した。イディラは生きている…治療を手配し、見張りをつけろ。もしまた歪みの影響に屈することあれば…警告せずに撃て」
languages.original_text: "I got rid of the psyker's creations. Idira is alive — see that she gets medical attention, and then put a guard on her. If she succumbs to the warp's influence again — shoot her without warning."

languages.text: "Ich habe die Schöpfungen der Psionikerin beseitigt. Idira lebt ... seht zu, dass sie medizinisch versorgt wird und lasst sie bewachen. Sollte sie dem Einfluss des Warps noch einmal erliegen ... erschießt sie ohne Vorwarnung."
languages.original_text: "I got rid of the psyker's creations. Idira is alive — see that she gets medical attention, and then put a guard on her. If she succumbs to the warp's influence again — shoot her without warning."

languages.text: « Les créations de la psyker sont hors d'état de nuire. Idira est en vie Veillez à ce qu'elle reçoive les soins nécessaires et placez-la sous surveillance. Si elle succombe à nouveau à l'influence du Warp, je veux qu'elle soit abattue sur-le-champ. »

languages.text: "Ruhsezerin yaratımlarından kurtuldum. İdira yaşıyor. Tıbbi yardım almasını sağlayın, başına da bir koruma dikin. Öteboyutun etkisine yeniden boyun eğerse onu oracıkta vurun."
